//this is an fullstack ecommerce app
This is social media like app-

Login User as an admin or as an normal user

Sigup User

Update Profile
 
Add Products/Edit Products

Product View/Product Rating & Comment

Checkout process (shipping, payment method, etc) - User can place a order (add to cart then add the shipping address then select the payment method and then do the payment)

Admin can update the order status(Mark the order as delivered when the order gets delivered)

Node Version : v16.1.0 npm version : 8.1.0

first run to install the dependencies
     npm install    

After this to run the project
     npm run dev
